Subject: [PATCH] Per world Canvas configs


diff --git a/net/minecraft/world/level/Level.java b/net/minecraft/world/level/Level.java
index 9145174c0f21154c4c0f41af0fbbac61b991edf5..9b0def2f71000fb7ee8f4853c4ba7b3baa86236e 100644
--- a/net/minecraft/world/level/Level.java
